{"tid":1547277,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[Twitter 文宣] 我係一個6月就有喺Twitter做日文文宣嘅香港人，想比巴絲們一d玩twitter嘅建議","createTime":"2019-09-06T15:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T23:20:45.000Z","uid":171804,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f54f77941e2d415e1b46b8d90d1e2414e2f9db70","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"(代開po)<br />\n連登巴絲大家好。我係一個一直有玩開日文twitter既香港人user，有過千日本人follower<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rcbf6TO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcbf6TO.jpg&h=e60491d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6月開始我就每日都tweet香港既事，每日都不斷收到「保重小心」「香港加油」等來自日本follower既回覆同dm，個人認識自己文宣得唔錯，所以想比d建議香港巴絲玩twitter（lock左ac所以唔自爆啦）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 不要只叫口號/轉發情報tweet，多d講你個人感受（用外文）</strong><br />\n<br />\n其實運動去到呢個時候文宣組都已經累積左好多follower，老實講唔需要每人都發同一樣野，集中rt文宣組就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。講多d個人感受，個人參與既經驗，反而會比人感受到呢場運動係每一個香港人都參與緊，係有血有肉唔只係紙上國際新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家對著身邊人都識講：佢淨係識IG講幾句支持運動既說話，到底佢有無去集會遊行架？同樣道理，外國follower同你素未謀面，鬼知你平時係未真係有去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以大家係去和平集會既時候多po幾張相，話比全世界知每一個香港人都出緊力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然啦咁樣會有被篤灰既風險所以我會lock左ac先做（本身我多外國follower所以lock左都會有人睇）但超和理非個d大家可以試下（eg係街見到口號/譯下d感人肺腑既連登post上去）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申小妹本身日文未去到可以談論時事既地步，所以主力出個人感受post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。個人認為成效唔錯，真心比外國人覺得engage埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 得閒同你follower講多謝你地仲未離棄我同香港</strong><br />\n<br />\n老實講，香港既事同佢地無切身既關係係難代入d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以呢個時候你同佢地講番聲多謝（唔係覆人，係你自己出post講），比佢地知道佢地講聲多謝香港人都會好感激佢地，咁就可以keep著有互動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 進化版：比佢地真真正正參與運動</strong><br />\n<br />\n固之然外國人自發掩眼等等既表態係好鼓舞人心，但外國人入面都有沉默既大多數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。佢地可能只會reply你話支持，但唔會出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候大家就要幫手帶佢地既聲音入香港人入面。有連登ac就幫手譯下佢地既msg上去。我自己無連登ac，但我有將follower既reply/dm寫哂上連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7k8HsO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7k8HsO.jpg&h=8c954372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總而言之，大家玩得twitter就玩得比人覺得貼地d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣先可以令外國人都覺得自己係#standwithhk<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n註：我見Twitter大部份香港人都想用graphic/meme等等去宣傳香港示威，但要明白唔係個個外國人都岩用meme去宣傳，因為佢地可能唔係呢種文化，尤其係上一輩（我自己follower入面真係有若干日本人係30年前親身睇住六四發生既年紀）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。如果你target係日本人/上一輩，回歸基本簡簡單單當寫下香港人日記，已經可以令佢地有共鳴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（呢個Twitter玩法係比累積左一定follower但又唔係主要情報翻譯user/無信心用外文深入解釋香港情況而又想係Twitter出一分力既巴絲參考。純粹個人經驗分享。）<br />\n<br />\n附上我自己做過既一個民調結果，回答者全部係我既日本follower。sample size唔大但可以參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OD9abkP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOD9abkP.jpg&h=797f717d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我問佢地只係想睇有關新聞既tweet，定係都想知淨係香港人先知既事（e.g.連登d post），發現好多人揀後者。其實佢地都想由本地香港人角度感受呢一件事，所以作為普通香港人大家可以寫下日記。"},{"pid":"312dd0579f0169a66c9f588328d6542c67fe636d","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"50253ab22462cb49227c4ecdc41fca09aae9d13c","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a8bc4db09b45bc95feda115a4737eb27d20d39c1","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"a7b3b4f7a9623bf05ee94ba1db745041c630f8d7","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:28:39.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"45c7883ecf08964c78e3745df49844811306d4e9","tid":1547277,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9715d854fdbbd7e28ac924acdf232ca47bbd2fd","tid":1547277,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"【正視聽】屌撚曬你地班連登仔 五毛支那仔混入連登撚9你地 仲有一千正皮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546979</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\np牌仔冇人理求幫推<br />\n有支那仔扮去美國見議員"},{"pid":"ae3e2f66e12bddd60f3ffd4142413c8888384ab3","tid":1547277,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主好有心"},{"pid":"a8b45961ef66f3cf027c899e569749b1cd4b84bf","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"339413b65f8a45a3ab8379a3627471275e132c67","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:31:56.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"1cce5942aadc9a4f16381b5562ddb9b8f41851f9","tid":1547277,"uid":93310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:32:01.000Z","msg":"高汁post lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204b7b74e3807faa5d818debc970e54f036a10f1","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"8f72fa1c2a2c7c436b60e6678589ef401c043c08","tid":1547277,"uid":271455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:33:48.000Z","msg":"我都剛剛開了twitter<br />\n我想問下，我又無follower，我去邊度寫野？我都去過CNN， BBC 寫。<br />\n<br />\n有沒有D 外國Twitter 介紹。我去follow，然後去寫？"},{"pid":"7e459d4dee3bd79c70471bc59fed8329a11cef5b","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"63f8939ffb831f08e455b4347b0f77feb385707f","tid":1547277,"uid":39842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱呀！大家係 Twitter 做文宣其中一個重點係互動！你要同 follower 有互動先做到 engagement <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSocial media 就係交朋友，交朋友係要攞個心出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aff17a649ca1aafe3a63bb6cf687c923c84e1d6","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:35:22.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"8559eab9a4b0baf026eda476c8a6cdedd86f2ec1","tid":1547277,"uid":195550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:35:41.000Z","msg":"我同意，有時候加少少個人意見都okay，可能有啲人英文麻麻就唔敢用英文去表達自己意見，但係我覺得唔使怕醜嘅，不論grammar錯也好點都好，唔使驚人地點諗，因為咁樣先係真正俾人地見到你嘅個人意見嘅！<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係英文好麻麻嘅，我個人覺得用中文都okay，但係當然文宣個效果會細咗。"},{"pid":"660faebbae5671e4601b947e2eebd443d2e06bc7","tid":1547277,"uid":47256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"72b842b2470e3b7a29798c203c2191fea9e1738e","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:37:57.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"e2fa530eb5088f0611c77ec4fa7ee3f74c3e750d","tid":1547277,"uid":137615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:43:15.000Z","msg":"用左twitter幾年，好開心香港終於有人用<br />\n<br />\n但我見而家d accounts/tweets個個都係呃followers<br />\n貼張女仔相 hashtag晒hongkongfollowback 話自己唔夠followers又盛<br />\n結果呢堆人就淨係識retweet<br />\n仲要tweets全部中文<br />\n我心諗你點文宣呀<br />\n<br />\n其實真心文宣未必要多followers<br />\n你去d news accounts comment/retweet，其他外國人就睇到<br />\n多d同外國人交流 先有文宣效果<br />\n一堆狗公/自己人互follow互retweet 圍爐取暖 冇意思"},{"pid":"7216e627fa896d76af6ebcfaaabd190cd685eba3","tid":1547277,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:54:18.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"1abb0ff69171907c8cd9459862d64325bbadec93","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f72fa1c2a2c7c436b60e6678589ef401c043c08","tid":1547277,"uid":271455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:33:48.000Z","msg":"我都剛剛開了twitter<br />\n我想問下，我又無follower，我去邊度寫野？我都去過CNN， BBC 寫。<br />\n<br />\n有沒有D 外國Twitter 介紹。我去follow，然後去寫？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"巴/絲打你好! 我明一開始玩twitter係會好淆, 其實我自己累積到咁多日本follower都唔係因為香港示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主可以試下用#Followbackhongkong搵下香港人互follow 雖然係圍爐多但最少確保你既tweet會比人睇到+RT<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外我構思緊一個「我係香港人，你問我答」(多國語言版) 既twitter campaign (遲D會再開post)，到時會比所有香港人容易D參與到twitter文宣 會再開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de02b34185a8cc6de2aab7b7b9b6d38ae6c86ef","tid":1547277,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:00:10.000Z","msg":"識日文冇入文宣組谷<br />\n我都係retweet完另外出個&gt;&gt;rt（意見）我咁嘅tweet就算<br />\n幫手推retweet同いいね數"},{"pid":"9f826d8007c5d75312a4283f9274fe1977404efc","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"我代frd回po ，有問題既話會盡快覆大家"},{"pid":"687175bd8ee74a476362db72e28e98cb2660187f","tid":1547277,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2fa530eb5088f0611c77ec4fa7ee3f74c3e750d","tid":1547277,"uid":137615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:43:15.000Z","msg":"用左twitter幾年，好開心香港終於有人用<br />\n<br />\n但我見而家d accounts/tweets個個都係呃followers<br />\n貼張女仔相 hashtag晒hongkongfollowback 話自己唔夠followers又盛<br />\n結果呢堆人就淨係識retweet<br />\n仲要tweets全部中文<br />\n我心諗你點文宣呀<br />\n<br />\n其實真心文宣未必要多followers<br />\n你去d news accounts comment/retweet，其他外國人就睇到<br />\n多d同外國人交流 先有文宣效果<br />\n一堆狗公/自己人互follow互retweet 圍爐取暖 冇意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"我完全明白巴/絲既說話 我都係見到有呢個現象覺得有D憂心做唔到文宣效果所以上黎開post 不過好多香港人都係twitter新手 好難怪想搵人圍下爐先 (其實咁樣都可以確保大家D ac唔係太5毛feel)<br />\n我絕對贊同比起圍爐更加要集中RT大型文宣組文宣/官方媒體 等全世界知香港既事係好大件事<br />\ntwitter新手要出產到有影響力既文宣 (有外國人睇) 其實唔容易<br />\n所以我覺得新手既話唔需要太介懷follower (夠人唔會比人當5毛清就OK) 多D去多謝外國人 多D RT官方新聞(外文) 就已經好夠"}]}